overview: The user initiated a review of their sleep questionnaire application
  to confirm it met all specified acceptance criteria. The assistant performed a
  comprehensive analysis, identifying both successfully implemented features and
  significant gaps. A detailed plan was then presented, prioritizing missing
  functionalities such as a tiredness severity scale, COMISA detection, and the
  inclusion of outbound links in reports. The assistant has begun executing this
  plan, starting with the implementation of the tiredness severity scale, which
  involved updating data types, validation schemas, and the user interface to
  include a slider and conditional safety warnings for high severity scores.
